1️⃣ IdentityHistory kya hai?
👉 IdentityHistory = user ke past actions ka record (audit log)
Matlab:-
user ne kya kiya
kab kiya
kisne kiya
➡ Sab history me store hota hai

✅ Example:-
User: Rahul
Actions:-
Role assign hua
Access revoke hua
Password reset hua
➡ Ye sab IdentityHistory me record hota hai

🔹 2️⃣ Ye kya karta hai?
👉 Ye track karta hai:-
changes in identity
access changes
provisioning events
approvals / rejections

🔹 3️⃣ Kya ye DB me store hota hai?
✅ Haan bhai, DB me store hota hai
📦 Structure:-
Identity (Rahul)
   ↓
IdentityHistory
   ↓
Event: Role Assigned
Time: 10:00 AM

🔹 4️⃣ Iske andar kya hota hai?
Field	       Meaning
eventType:-----kya action hua
timestamp:-----kab hua
performedBy:---kisne kiya
target:--------kis pe action hua
details:-------extra info

🔹 5️⃣ Important Methods:-
🔸 Event Info:-
getEventType() → event type deta hai (Role Assigned, Access Removed)
setEventType(String type) → event type set karta hai
🔸 Time:-
getTimestamp() → kab event hua
setTimestamp(Date time) → time set karta hai
🔸 Actor:-
getPerformedBy() → kisne action kiya
setPerformedBy(String user) → performer set karta hai
🔸 Target:-
getTarget() → kis identity pe action hua
setTarget(String target) → target set karta hai
🔸 Details:-
getDetails() → extra info deta hai
setDetails(String details) → details set karta hai
🔸 Utility:-
toString() → readable string
equals(Object obj) → compare karta hai
hashCode() → hash generate karta hai.

🚀 🔥 Full Code (SailPointContext ke saath):-
import sailpoint.api.SailPointContext;
import sailpoint.api.SailPointFactory;
import sailpoint.object.IdentityHistory;
import java.util.Date;

public class HistoryExample {

    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {

        SailPointContext context = SailPointFactory.getCurrentContext();

        IdentityHistory history = new IdentityHistory();

        // Event
        history.setEventType("Role Assigned");

        // Time
        history.setTimestamp(new Date());

        // Actor
        history.setPerformedBy("Admin");

        // Target
        history.setTarget("Rahul");

        // Details
        history.setDetails("Admin Role assigned to Rahul");

        // Print
        System.out.println(history.getEventType());
        System.out.println(history.getTimestamp());
        System.out.println(history.getPerformedBy());
        System.out.println(history.getTarget());
        System.out.println(history.getDetails());

        // Save
        context.saveObject(history);
        context.commitTransaction();

        System.out.println("✅ History Saved");
    }
}
📤 Output:-
Role Assigned
Thu Mar 27 12:30:00 IST 2026
Admin
Rahul
Admin Role assigned to Rahul
✅ History Saved